Hannah New https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_New 0 Hannah New is an English actress and model. She is known for her starring role on the television show Black Sails in which she plays Eleanor Guthrie, the owner of a saloon in Nassau and for her role as Rosalinda Fox in The Time in Between.
